### Simple GET — JSON response
# Place the cursor anywhere inside this block and run :Rest run
GET https://api.lais.app/api/v2/chats/6865d1dd4cab732015dff6d3/6865d24f0f48329de28f2439/lista-by-status?status=Pendente&limit=100&setor_id=6865d1f922d17c67273fa91a
Accept: application/json

### GET with query params + custom header
GET https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts/1
Accept: application/json
X-Demo-Header: rest.nvim

### POST with JSON body
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "rest.nvim",
  "version": "v2.0.1",
  "lang": "lua"
}

### POST form-encoded
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=renato&editor=neovim

### PUT request
PUT https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "updated",
  "body": "patched via rest.nvim",
  "userId": 1
}

### DELETE request
DELETE https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts/1

### Variables — set once, reuse across requests
@base = https://httpbin.org
@token = secret-test-token

### Use the variables above
GET {{base}}/headers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Inspect status codes
GET https://httpbin.org/status/404

### Slow response — useful to see rest.nvim's timing
GET https://httpbin.org/delay/2
